data.description: Sellers are very motivited.  Come and see this nice open floor plan 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bath with 2 car garage and master bedroom down, of single owner and well maintained property on a stablished community. Newly painted inside with nice and new laminate floors with water softener.  All carpeted areas will be replace.  It's 6.5 miles to University Hospital and Medical Center.  Close to Bandera Rd and 1604, malls, shopping areas, and restaurants.  Elementary school is about a mile, and middle school, high school and UTSA is approximately 3.5 miles away. Easy access to major highways and very close to La Cantera Mall and Fiesta Texas Park, Costco and Sam's Club.
